text: Iolanda is a given name used in Italian, Portuguese and Romanian languages. Notable persons with this name include: * Iolanda Balaș (1936–2016), a Romanian Olympic athlete and high jumper * Iolanda Fleming (born 1936), Brazilian professor and politician * Iolanda Gigliotti (1933–1987), known as Dalida, French vocalist and actress == See also == * Asteroid 509 Iolanda * Yolanda (disambiguation) == References == Category:Italian feminine given names Category:Portuguese feminine given names Category:Romanian feminine given names
title: Iolanda
